  <h1>Submit a Tip</h1>
  <p>Know about something happening in your neighborhood that we should cover? We want to hear about it.</p>
  <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a> with a brief description of the tip and, if possible, a public source we can verify it against.</p>
  <p>We read every tip. We can't respond to all of them, but every verifiable tip is considered for the next issue of the relevant cluster.</p>
  <h2>What makes a good tip</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Something happening in a specific neighborhood</li>
    <li>A public meeting, construction project, business opening or closing, or community event</li>
    <li>A city agency announcement that affects residents</li>
    <li>A link to a public source we can verify against</li>
  </ul>
</div></div></main>
